flowchart TD
    S[Start] --> R1[Run Universe Research]
    R1 --> G{Guardrails OK?}
    G -- yes --> CL[Concentration Limits (per symbol / per (symbol,strategy))]
    G -- no --> W[Warn + Mark not OK]
    W --> CL
    CL --> P[Persist Results + Refresh best_configs]
    P --> D[Dashboard (auto-open once)]
    D --> C{Scheduler? --repeat-mins>0}
